Package model

This package contains the classes that define the models for representing the information managed by the application.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuoyDatabase
    This class is to manage the connection and queries with the database that stores the information of the buoys.
    DatasetFile
    This class defines the model for representing the information of an intermediate or pre-processed dataset file.
    HistoricalFile
    This class defines the model for representing the information of an historical file of a buoy.
    Instance
    This class defines the model for representing an instance or set of measurements collected by a buoy in a specific date and time.
    InstancesWeka
    This class defines the model for representing in WEKA format a set of instances of a buoy.
    MatchingFinalDataset
    This class defines the model for representing the information of a final dataset.
    PreprocessDatasetFile
    This class defines the model for pre-processing the information of an intermediate or pre-processed dataset file.
    ReanalysisDatabase
    This class is to manage the connection and queries with the database that stores the information of the reanalysis data files.
    ReanalysisFile
    This class defines the model to manage a reanalysis data file and represent the information stored on it.
    RecoveringFilters
    This class defines the model for applying recovering data tasks over the information of an intermediate or pre-processed dataset file.

Package model Description

This package contains the classes that define the models for representing the information managed by the application.
